foundry-desktop (1.0.2) resolute; urgency=medium

  * Move foundry-create-usb.sh to /usr/bin/ (was /usr/local/bin/).
    Packages must not ship files in /usr/local/ per Debian policy.

 -- Foundry Linux <packages@foundrylinux.org>  Wed, 04 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000

foundry-desktop (1.0.1) resolute; urgency=medium

  * Ship foundry-create-usb.sh (/usr/bin/) and create-foundry-usb.desktop
    (/usr/share/applications/): one-click USB stick creator. Downloads the
    latest anvil ISO, verifies sha256, launches isoimagewriter. Supports
    --iso PATH --device /dev/sdX for headless dd write (used by task iso-write).
  * Add Depends: isoimagewriter | usb-creator-kde, kdialog.

 -- Foundry Linux <packages@foundrylinux.org>  Wed, 04 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000

foundry-desktop (1.0.0) resolute; urgency=medium

  * Initial release. Collects KDE-specific Foundry Linux packages
    (foundry-welcome, foundry-kde-theme) into an explicit metapackage.
    ISO users get this via foundry-anvil; existing Ubuntu users skip it.
    See docs/plans/2026-05-28-foundry-core-desktop-split.md.

 -- Foundry Linux <packages@foundrylinux.org>  Wed, 28 May 2026 00:00:00 +0700
